name: C series 002: Sea Angel
description:
Artists interpretation of a 'Sea Angel'.  Old Ahab fell into the sea once on a trawl and they thought they had lost him.  He was under for long enough to drown a few times over.  When they finally pulled him out he kept babbling about a 'Sea Angel'.  He insists something was pulling him down and that this 'angel' saved him.  Maybe it was the rum and the shock but who knows… 
Special OBJKT4OBJKT piece
